defaultWe have of course raised the question as to whether ASHPs should qualify for tax payer funded subsidy given that their performance in closely monitored trials over long periods has repeatedly failed to meet the requirements of the Renewa
defaultble Energy Directive
default meaning the energy they generate could not be counted towards the UK’s renewable targets
