defaultThe Zero Carbon Hub identifies heat pumps as demonstrating a performance gap between stated and actual installed building performance: “There are concerns regarding the level of both installation and comm
defaultissioning skills for building services, especially mechanical ventilation and heat pumps as demonstrated by GHA research, Zero Carbon Hub’s Ventilation and Indoor Air Quality reports and EST field trial,” (
